<p><img class="aligncenter" title="rag_and_bone_fall_2016" src="http://i1142.photobucket.com/albums/n612/chicityfashion/16/rag%20bone%20jeans.jpg" alt="" width="683" height="1024" border="0" /></p>
<p>Rag &amp; Bone is just dipping their toes in the water that is see now buy now&#8230;as they&#8217;re offering <a href="http://bit.ly/1UcbtcC" target="_blank">one pair of jeans</a> from their Fall &#8217;16 collection (which I&#8217;m <em>very</em> interested in, by the way).</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" title="michael_kors_bag" src="http://i1142.photobucket.com/albums/n612/chicityfashion/16/mk%20stud%20bag.jpg" alt="" width="683" height="1024" border="0" /></p>
<p>Michael Kors has <a href="http://bit.ly/1QoYuVh" target="_blank">quite a few Fall options</a> you can shop now, including a variety of clothing, bags and shoes (which are much edgier than I originally gave MK credit for&#8230;even though the studded sweater totally looks like Wang).</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" title="michael_kors_runway" src="http://i1142.photobucket.com/albums/n612/chicityfashion/16/mk%20stud%20sweater.jpg" alt="" width="683" height="1024" border="0" /></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" title="michael_kors_runway_bag" src="http://i1142.photobucket.com/albums/n612/chicityfashion/16/mk%20spotted%20bag.jpg" alt="" width="683" height="1024" border="0" /></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" title="shop_michael_kors_runway" src="http://i1142.photobucket.com/albums/n612/chicityfashion/16/michael%20kors%20sweater.jpg" alt="" width="683" height="1024" border="0" /></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" title="michael_kors_fall_2016" src="http://i1142.photobucket.com/albums/n612/chicityfashion/16/michael%20kors%20feather%20outfit.jpg" alt="" width="683" height="1024" border="0" /></p>
<p>You can get all these looks below and on the <a href="http://bit.ly/1QoYuVh" target="_blank">Michael Kors website</a>.</p>
