y, you&#8217;re going to be PUMPED about this week&#8217;s episode of Fashion Friends. If it can be used on your hair, skin and / or nails&#8230;my latest guest has probably tried it. Get inside the head of Glossier Editor, Emily Ferber, RIGHT HERE (or right here) right now. [&#8230;]</p>
