<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-17803 size-full" title="stylecaster_creative_director" src="http://chicityfashion.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/melissa1.png" alt="melissa medvedich" width="2400" height="2400" srcset="http://chicityfashion.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/melissa1-50x50.png 50w, http://chicityfashion.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/melissa1-610x610.png 610w, http://chicityfashion.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/melissa1-768x768.png 768w, http://chicityfashion.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/melissa1-600x600.png 600w, http://chicityfashion.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/melissa1-180x180.png 180w, http://chicityfashion.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/melissa1-470x470.png 470w, http://chicityfashion.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/melissa1-150x150.png 150w, http://chicityfashion.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/melissa1.png 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 2400px) 100vw, 2400px" /><span id="more-17801"></span></p>
<p>If you frequent <a href="http://stylecaster.com" target="_blank">StyleCaster.com</a>, you probably noticed they recently got a makeover&#8230;and that&#8217;s all thanks to this week&#8217;s Fashion Friend, Melissa Medvedich. In episode 20, we&#8217;ll be discussing this coming NYFW (lots of changes happening&#8230;<a href="http://chicityfashion.com/fashion-week-changes/" target="_blank">yet again</a>). We&#8217;ll also answer [what I&#8217;m deeming] the question of 2016 &#8212; are blogs over? There&#8217;s a reason I&#8217;m asking, but you&#8217;ll have to tune in to find out why. And because you already know my favorite<a href="http://chicityfashion.com/under-the-radar-beauty-brands/" target="_blank"> under the radar beauty brands</a> (and Melissa happens to be a fellow beauty junkie) you&#8217;ll get to find out her favorites (which you&#8217;ve probably never heard of&#8230;so pay close attention!) After all that fun stuff, we&#8217;ll get into even more fun stuff&#8230;like how Melissa got into fashion, what she did before StyleCaster, and what we can look forward to from them, as well as some solid info you can take away like what <em>really</em> makes for a good website, how YOU can become a creative director..and more.</p>
<p>Listen below / <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/fashion-friends/id994512359?mt=2&amp;ls=1" target="_blank">subscribe on iTunes</a>. Don’t forget to let me know what you think about this week’s episode (and the slightly new format) in the comments. Hope you enjoyed our conversation, and be on the look out for my next fashion friend&#8230;coming soon!</p>

